data.description: Desirable and beautiful LAKES BY THE BAY Home featuring 3 beds, 2 baths and 1 car garage. This home has a gorgeous high ceilings, open concept, remodeled kitchen with dark cabinets, granite counter tops, brand new stainless steel appliances, huge pantry and breakfast area. Spacious master bedroom with sliding doors leading to your backyard. New pergola and shed. Remodeled bathrooms.Brand new washer and dryer. Brand new water heater (2019), New AC installed 2019 and Digital thermostat, new electric panel installed 2019, New roof 2020. Centrally located right off of OLD CUTLER RD. Easy commute to Homestead Reserve Base, Turkey Point Power Plant, Miami and the Fl Keys.
